title: Rush - Work In Progress - 320k - MP3
description:
RUSH
"Work In Progress"
320k 44.1khz Lame HQ MP3

Description:
This unofficial release is the entire "Test for Echo" album with re-recorded live drum parts from Neil Peart's A Work In Progress Instructional Drum DVD which results in a slightly different sounding mix as well.  The tracklist is the preserved in order as played from the source.  The sound quality is very good.  I would classify this as for the most diehard Rush fans only!
